OL,3,C'A big question to live with': Would
OL,4,Cyou want to know if you could get
OL,5,Cdementia?
OL,7,F"Mum used to say, 'I'm going to get
OL,8,Fthis one day. I don't want it, I just
OL,9,Fdon't want what happened to the rest
OL,10,Fof the family.'" Matthew said.
OL,12,F"It was hard to hear her say that
OL,13,Fbecause deep down, I think she knew."
OL,15,FWhen dementia develops before the age
OL,16,Fof 65, it's known as Young Onset
OL,17,FDementia.
