OL,3,C'A big question to live with': Would
OL,4,Cyou want to know if you could get
OL,5,Cdementia?
OL,7,FA 22 year-old Norwich man is thought
OL,8,Fto be the youngest man in the UK
OL,9,Fliving with the disease. According to
OL,10,FAlzheimer's Research UK, he is one of
OL,11,Fmore than 70,000 people in the UK who
OL,12,Fare living with young onset dementia.
OL,14,FAlthough memory loss is often the
OL,15,Ffirst symptom people associate with
OL,16,Fdementia, it can look very different
OL,17,Fin people under 65. Early symptoms can
OL,18,Finclude confusion, difficulty finding
OL,19,Fwords, trouble recognising familiar
OL,20,Fobjects, and losing interest in
OL,21,Fhobbies.
