OL,3,C'A big question to live with': Would
OL,4,Cyou want to know if you could get
OL,5,Cdementia?
OL,7,FDespite being a silent illness,
OL,8,Fdementia has increasingly made
OL,9,Fheadlines in recent years. In 2023,
OL,10,FITV journalist Fiona Phillips spoke
OL,11,Fpublicly about her diagnosis at just
OL,12,F62 years old.
OL,14,FSince his mother's passing, Matthew
OL,15,Fhas been thinking more about what lies
OL,16,Fahead. He is now considering whether
OL,17,Fto take a genetic test that could tell
OL,18,Fhim if he carries the same genetic
OL,19,Fmutation that runs through his family,
OL,20,Fand whether he's likely to develop
OL,21,Fdementia himself.
