OL,3,C'A big question to live with': Would
OL,4,Cyou want to know if you could get
OL,5,Cdementia?
OL,7,FMatthew, a musician and performer,
OL,8,Fsays the uncertainty can feel
OL,9,Foverwhelming.
OL,11,F"It's a really big question to live
OL,12,Fwith," he said. "I think about it all
OL,13,Fthe time. There's a chance I could get
OL,14,Fit, and part of me feels I should know
OL,15,F` but another part of me isn't sure I
OL,16,Fcould handle that."
