OL,3,C'A big question to live with': Would
OL,4,Cyou want to know if you could get
OL,5,Cdementia?
OL,7,F"I've been looking into the tests,"
OL,8,FMatthew said. "You think, if I find
OL,9,Fout, do I live my life differently? Or
OL,10,Fdo I just spend years worrying? I
OL,11,Fstill don't know what the right answer
OL,12,Fis."
OL,14,FMatthew and his partner, Alex, are
OL,15,Fthinking about starting a family,
OL,16,Feither through IVF or adoption, but
OL,17,Fthe uncertainty about Matthew's future
OL,18,Fhas forced some difficult
OL,19,Fconversations.
