OL,3,C'A big question to live with': Would
OL,4,Cyou want to know if you could get
OL,5,Cdementia?
OL,7,FThe Welsh Government has faced growing
OL,8,Fpressure to publish a new Dementia
OL,9,FAction Plan after the previous one
OL,10,Fexpired in 2022. Politicians from
OL,11,Facross the Senedd have urged ministers
OL,12,Fto act quickly, warning that people
OL,13,Fliving with dementia are being failed
OL,14,Fby the current system. A public
OL,15,Fconsultation on a new plan is expected
OL,16,Flater this year.
