OL,3,C'A big question to live with': Would
OL,4,Cyou want to know if you could get
OL,5,Cdementia?
OL,7,FDr Catrin Hedd Jones, a dementia
OL,8,Fspecialist and adviser to the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment, says stories like
OL,10,FMatthew's show how urgently Wales
OL,11,Fneeds consistent support and better
OL,12,Faccess to early diagnosis.
OL,14,F"My hope is that the government will
OL,15,Fmove forward with the next action
OL,16,Fplan. I think it's great that they're
OL,17,Fconsulting, but we want that next
OL,18,Fconsultation to start now," she said.
