OL,3,C'A big question to live with': Would
OL,4,Cyou want to know if you could get
OL,5,Cdementia?
OL,7,F"My big concern is that, with next
OL,8,Fyear's Senedd Election, the
OL,9,Fconsultation will take us into the
OL,10,Fspring, and we won't see anything
OL,11,Fhappening again until well into
OL,12,Fanother year. So now is the time for
OL,13,Four government to put more emphasis on
OL,14,Fgetting the next action plan out."
