OL,3,C'A big question to live with': Would
OL,4,Cyou want to know if you could get
OL,5,Cdementia?
OL,7,FMatthew will share his story in an
OL,8,Fepisode of Y Byd ar Bedwar on Monday
OL,9,Fnight, which will explore the impact
OL,10,Fof young onset dementia on individuals
OL,11,Fand their families.
OL,13,FHe's now using his music to raise
OL,14,Fawareness of dementia, performing a
OL,15,Fnew song, Psychic, written in memory
OL,16,Fof his mother, and donating proceeds
OL,17,Fto research charities.
OL,19,F"It's been in my family for decades,"
OL,20,Fhe said. "I just hope one day, we find
OL,21,Fa cure."
